---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="HVAC Services in String Prairie, TX | String Prairie Heating & Air"
	description="Local heating and air conditioning services in String Prairie, Texas. Family-owned HVAC company providing installation, repair, and maintenance in String Prairie and surrounding Bastrop County."
>
	<section class="page-header">
		<div class="container">
			<h1>HVAC Services in String Prairie, TX</h1>
			<p>Your hometown heating and air conditioning experts</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="area-content">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="area-intro">
				<h2>Proudly Serving Our Home Community of String Prairie</h2>
				<p class="lead">
					String Prairie Heating & Air is proud to call String Prairie home. As your neighbors in this beautiful rural Bastrop County community, we understand the unique HVAC challenges that come with country living. From the historic farms and ranches along the winding country roads to the newer homes being built in the area, we're committed to keeping String Prairie families comfortable year-round.
				</p>
				<p class="lead">
					Our company name reflects our deep roots in this community. When you call String Prairie Heating & Air, you're not just getting an HVAC contractor - you're getting a neighbor who takes pride in serving the community we call home. We provide fast, reliable heating and cooling services to every corner of String Prairie and the surrounding countryside.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="areas-served">
				<h3>Areas We Serve in String Prairie</h3>
				<p>
					We provide HVAC services throughout the String Prairie community including properties along FM 20, rural homesteads near Rosanky Road, ranches and farms throughout the String Prairie area, homes along Highway 304, and all surrounding acreage. As a local company based right here in String Prairie, we can respond quickly to your heating and cooling needs.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="services-overview">
				<h2>Complete HVAC Services for String Prairie Homes & Businesses</h2>
				<div class="services-list">
					<div class="service-item">
						<h3>Air Conditioning</h3>
						<p>AC installation, repair, maintenance, and emergency service to keep you cool during hot Texas summers.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="service-item">
						<h3>Heating Systems</h3>
						<p>Furnace and heat pump installation, repair, and maintenance for comfortable winters.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="service-item">
						<h3>Maintenance Plans</h3>
						<p>Preventive maintenance to extend system life, improve efficiency, and prevent breakdowns.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="service-item">
						<h3>Emergency Service</h3>
						<p>Fast response when you need it most - we're just down the road and ready to help.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="local-advantages">
				<h2>Why String Prairie Residents Choose Their Local HVAC Company</h2>
				<ul class="advantage-list">
					<li>Based right here in String Prairie - we're your neighbors</li>
					<li>Fastest response times in the area - just minutes away</li>
					<li>Deep understanding of rural property HVAC needs</li>
					<li>Honest, transparent pricing with no hidden fees</li>
					<li>Fully licensed and insured for your protection</li>
					<li>Expert knowledge of Central Texas climate challenges</li>
					<li>Quality workmanship backed by solid warranties</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<div class="map-section">
				<h2>Find Us on the Map</h2>
				<p class="map-subtitle">Proudly based in String Prairie, serving our home community</p>
				<div class="map-container">
					<iframe
						src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d55187.36!2d-97.33!3d29.89!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x864363e7a4f3e4ed%3A0x1f7670034fca8de3!2sString%20Prairie%2C%20TX!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1234567890"
						width="100%"
						height="450"
						style="border:0; border-radius: 12px;"
						allowfullscreen=""
						loading="lazy"
						referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade">
					</iframe>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="testimonials-section">
				<h2>What String Prairie Customers Say</h2>
				<p class="testimonials-subtitle">Hear from your neighbors about their experience with String Prairie Heating & Air</p>
				<div class="testimonials-grid">
					<div class="testimonial-card">
						<div class="stars">*****</div>
						<p class="testimonial-text">"It's so nice having an HVAC company right here in String Prairie. Ron and his team are true professionals and always go above and beyond. Being local makes such a difference - they understand our community!"</p>
						<p class="testimonial-author">- James M., String Prairie</p>
					</div>
					<div class="testimonial-card">
						<div class="stars">*****</div>
						<p class="testimonial-text">"When our AC went out during a heat wave, String Prairie Heating & Air was at our house within the hour. Can't beat that kind of local service! They had us back up and running the same day."</p>
						<p class="testimonial-author">- Patricia S., String Prairie</p>
					</div>
					<div class="testimonial-card">
						<div class="stars">*****</div>
						<p class="testimonial-text">"We've used String Prairie for all our HVAC needs since they opened. They're honest, reliable, and do quality work. It's great supporting a local business that takes care of its community."</p>
						<p class="testimonial-author">- Robert & Linda C., String Prairie</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="review-cta">
					<a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/String+Prairie+Heating+%26+Air/@29.8918229,-97.3320232" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="review-link">Leave us a Google Review</a>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="cta-section-local">
				<h2>Schedule Your HVAC Service in String Prairie</h2>
				<p>Ready for reliable HVAC service from your hometown experts? Contact us today!</p>
				<div class="cta-buttons">
					<a href="https://book.housecallpro.com/book/String-Prairie-Heating--Air/df82ded280ce43f4a9ee6ee6d36aef76?v2=true" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary">Book Online</a>
					<a href="tel:5129249744" class="btn btn-secondary">Call (512) 924-9744</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.page-header {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark-blue) 0%, var(--primary-blue) 100%);
		color: white;
		padding: 5rem 0;
		text-align: center;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.page-header h1 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
	}

	.page-header p {
		font-size: 1.35rem;
		opacity: 0.95;
		font-weight: 300;
	}

	.area-content {
		padding: 5rem 0;
	}

	.area-intro {
		max-width: 850px;
		margin: 0 auto 4rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.area-intro h2 {
		color: var(--dark-blue);
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
	}

	.lead {
		font-size: 1.15rem;
		color: var(--text-dark);
		line-height: 1.8;
		font-weight: 300;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.areas-served {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-blue) 0%, var(--dark-blue) 100%);
		color: white;
		padding: 2.5rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.areas-served h3 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.areas-served p {
		line-height: 1.8;
		font-weight: 300;
		opacity: 0.95;
	}

	.services-overview {
		margin: 4rem 0;
	}

	.services-overview h2 {
		color: var(--dark-blue);
		font-size: 2.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
		text-align: center;
		font-weight: 800;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
	}

	.services-list {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.service-item {
		background: var(--bg-light);
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		border-left: 5px solid var(--accent-red);
		transition: all 0.3s;
	}

	.service-item:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(41, 94, 147, 0.12);
		border-left-color: var(--primary-blue);
	}

	.service-item h3 {
		color: var(--primary-blue);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.service-item p {
		color: var(--text-dark);
		line-height: 1.7;
		font-weight: 300;
	}

	.local-advantages {
		background: var(--bg-light);
		padding: 4rem 3rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		margin: 4rem 0;
	}

	.local-advantages h2 {
		color: var(--dark-blue);
		font-size: 2.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		text-align: center;
		font-weight: 800;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
	}

	.advantage-list {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		max-width: 750px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.advantage-list li {
		padding: 1rem 0 1rem 2.5rem;
		position: relative;
		color: var(--text-dark);
		font-weight: 300;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(41, 94, 147, 0.1);
	}

	.advantage-list li:last-child {
		border-bottom: none;
	}

	.advantage-list li:before {
		content: "âœ“";
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: var(--accent-red);
		font-weight: bold;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
	}

	.map-section {
		margin: 4rem 0;
		padding: 4rem 3rem;
		background: var(--bg-light);
		border-radius: 12px;
	}

	.map-section h2 {
		color: var(--dark-blue);
		font-size: 2.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		text-align: center;
		font-weight: 800;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
	}

	.map-subtitle {
		text-align: center;
		color: var(--text-light);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 300;
	}

	.map-container {
		max-width: 1000px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
		border-radius: 12px;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.testimonials-section {
		margin: 4rem 0;
	}

	.testimonials-section h2 {
		color: var(--dark-blue);
		font-size: 2.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		text-align: center;
		font-weight: 800;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
	}

	.testimonials-subtitle {
		text-align: center;
		color: var(--text-light);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		font-weight: 300;
	}

	.testimonials-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
		gap: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.testimonial-card {
		background: white;
		padding: 2.5rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
		border-left: 5px solid var(--accent-red);
		transition: all 0.3s;
	}

	.testimonial-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(41, 94, 147, 0.12);
		border-left-color: var(--primary-blue);
	}

	.stars {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		letter-spacing: 2px;
		color: #f59e0b;
	}

	.testimonial-text {
		color: var(--text-dark);
		line-height: 1.8;
		font-weight: 300;
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		font-style: italic;
	}

	.testimonial-author {
		color: var(--primary-blue);
		font-weight: 700;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
	}

	.review-cta {
		text-align: center;
	}

	.review-link {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-blue) 0%, var(--dark-blue) 100%);
		color: white;
		text-decoration: none;
		border-radius: 50px;
		font-weight: 700;
		font-size: 1rem;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
		transition: all 0.3s;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(41, 94, 147, 0.3);
	}

	.review-link:hover {
		transform: translateY(-3px);
		box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(41, 94, 147, 0.4);
	}

	.cta-section-local {
		text-align: center;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-red) 0%, var(--dark-red) 100%);
		color: white;
		padding: 4rem 3rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
	}

	.cta-section-local h2 {
		font-size: 2.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
	}

	.cta-section-local p {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		opacity: 0.95;
		font-weight: 300;
	}

	.cta-buttons {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		justify-content: center;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	.btn {
		padding: 1.25rem 2.5rem;
		border-radius: 50px;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 700;
		transition: all 0.3s;
		display: inline-block;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.5px;
		font-size: 1rem;
	}

	.btn-primary {
		background: white;
		color: var(--accent-red);
		box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
	}

	.btn-primary:hover {
		transform: translateY(-3px);
		box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
	}

	.btn-secondary {
		background: transparent;
		color: white;
		border: 2px solid white;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
	}

	.btn-secondary:hover {
		background: white;
		color: var(--accent-red);
		transform: translateY(-3px);
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.page-header h1 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.area-intro h2,
		.services-overview h2,
		.local-advantages h2,
		.map-section h2,
		.testimonials-section h2,
		.cta-section-local h2 {
			font-size: 1.75rem;
		}

		.services-list {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.map-section {
			padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
		}

		.testimonials-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.cta-buttons {
			flex-direction: column;
		}
	}
</style>
